    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and represents the absolute pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior is virtually flawless, with a deep, showroom-quality shine and no visible imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it was manufactured, offering a smooth, powerful, and whisper-quiet driving experience. Every feature and electronic component functions perfectly, and the service history is comprehensive, documenting a life of preventative maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in climate-controlled storage and treated with the utmost respect.",
