    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Characterized by robust mechanical performance and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers an exceptional balance of luxury and proven dependability. The interior remains in superior condition, reflecting a history of consistent care and professional oversight. This is a vetted asset, prepared for immediate acquisition and long-term service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
