    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and still runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway! It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, so you can just hop in and hit the road. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make its next owner super happy. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54 inline-six. This unit features crisp throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and precise Double VANOS timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts smoothly, sending power to a tight limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with reinforced subframe points and refreshed bushings. Recent service includes a full valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the internal tolerances are within factory specifications. It\u2019s an engaging, analog driving experience for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Maintenance records available. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though keen eyes will notice a few minor door dings and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery is in great shape with only minor wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button and feature, from the heated seats to the navigation system, works exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs quiet and strong, backed by a complete service history showing consistent oil changes and a recent cooling system flush. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a well-sorted, dependable car that drives as good as it looks.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior, this model balances consistent performance with sophisticated aesthetics. Our rigorous inspection process ensures that all primary mechanical systems operate at peak efficiency, offering a reliable and refined driving experience. Secure this exceptional value today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got a few signs of love here and there, but honestly, it\u2019s a fantastic ride that you\u2019re going to have a blast with. Perfect for daily commutes or a fun weekend road trip! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain features the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for maximum traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping characteristics for varied road conditions. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the longevity of its precision-engineered internals. Finished with the weight-saving carbon fiber roof, this M3 offers the visceral, high-induction-noise experience sought after by purists.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
